#. </h1></div><blockquote class="gatha"><p><a class="sc" id="1"></a><a
#. class="verse-num-sc" id="verse-num-sc207"></a><a class="verse-num-pts"
#. id="verse-num-pts207"></a><a class="pts" id="pts27"></a>
msgctxt "thag2.44:5.1"
msgid "“Chavipāpaka cittabhaddaka,"
msgstr "“Your skin is nasty but your heart is good,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag2.44:5.2"
msgid "Mogharāja satataṃ samāhito;"
msgstr "Mogharāja, you always have samādhi."

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag2.44:5.3"
msgid "<span class=\"var\" title=\"hemantikakālarattiyo (mr)\" id=\"note139\">Hemantikasītakālarattiyo</span>,"
msgstr "But in the nights of winter, so dark and cold,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag2.44:5.4"
msgid "Bhikkhu tvaṃsi kathaṃ karissasi”."
msgstr "How will you get by, monk?”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="2"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc208"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts208"></a>
msgctxt "thag2.44:6.1"
msgid "“Sampannasassā magadhā,"
msgstr "“I’ve heard that all the Magadhans"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag2.44:6.2"
msgid "kevalā iti me sutaṃ;"
msgstr "Have an abundance of grain."

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag2.44:6.3"
msgid "Palālacchannako seyyaṃ,"
msgstr "I’ll make my bed under a thatched roof,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag2.44:6.4"
msgid "yathaññe sukhajīvino”ti."
msgstr "Just like those who live in comfort.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta">
